= Entities =
Strangely, normal entities occur in this level despite its unstable nature. They are scattered in different places and wander randomly to find prey. The way they managed to enter or appear in this level is unknown.
= Entrances & Exits =
=<small> Entrances </small>=
*Entrances to this level may appear in random levels unpredictably.
=<small> Exits </small>=
*Noclip through a section that resembles the level one came from can bring them back to that Level.
*Wandering too far in this level leads one to the Broken.
